window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The pride will rise....</b></p> <p>My life changed dramatically ever since I found out that I’m a long-lost lion shifter, complete with awesome magic and special abilities. Being the only male lion shifter in Thornveil City comes with a few perks of its own, and my new celebrity status means that everyone wants to know what I’ll do next.</p> <p>That includes Roxanne Deveraux, the bombshell kitsune heiress, who has a surprise proposal that leaves me hot under the collar.</p> <p>But new power always brings new enemies. With Cyrus dead, a more powerful boss steps in, one that wants to drag the city back to its primordial roots.</p> <p>No matter how many people have to die in the process.</p> <p>The lion shifters have returned. Now my enemies will hear me roar.</p>"; 
